Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT u.Id, u.Username, u.Password, u.UserTypeId, u.Status, p.Address, p.BirthDate, p.CivilStatusId, p.ContactNo, p.EmailAddress, p.FirstName, p.Gender, p.Height, p.LastName, p.MiddleName, p.Occupation, p.PatientId, p.Weight FROM [User] as u INNER JOIN [PatientInformation] as p ON u.Id = p.PatientId WHERE u.Status = 1
